// =============================================================================
// SYSTEM LOCK OVERLAY — full-screen blocker that fires when the local
// network is unreachable or the system clock skews from the server time
// by more than 5 minutes. Pinned with z-index above every other modal so
// it hard-locks the entire UI; the only escape is to fix the underlying
// problem and click RETRY (which bumps the health-check nonce).
